 * Computer Architecture Layer
 ------------------------------
 
 - Abstraction : To take a relatively complex system and simplify it for our use. We have a mouse, keyboard to use and
 interact with the computer system without having to know and understand the underlying technical details. (under the hood)
 
 - undelying implementation of the technology.
 
 - Error Message - helps us identify the bug;
 
 - Computer Architecture Overview
 ---------------------------------
 4 main layers
 1. Hardware - physical components of a computer;
 2. Operating System - allows hardware to communicate with the system;
 3. Software - humans interact with computers;
 4. Users - Interacts with a computer - operate, program , etc;
 
